data.name: Donate_Instructions_Desc
data.value:
You can donate money to the project through our PayPal account. There is no minimum amount for your donation, but keep in mind that PayPal charges us a fee for each donation.
If you click on one of the buttons below, you will be taken to the secure PayPal website. You don't need to have a PayPal account in order to make a donation.
As a contributor to Aya, you receive a product key that disables the donation prompt, which is displayed from time to time in the application.
